```
***
$$
Error_i = y_i - \hat{y}
\\

Error_i^2  = (y_i - \hat{y})^2
\\
\text{- sum of the square of the residuals (SSE)}
\\
SSE  = \sum_{i=1}^{n}(y_i-\hat{y})^2
$$



